dd.1 
</b></p>
<p><b>562 </b><i>Para Country Date Type Mandate Allegations transmitted Government response 
</i></p>
<p>of obtaining a confession from him.   
</p>
<p>Moreover, while Mr. Attayiar was detained in 
the police station of Bir Bacha, between the 27 
